{{otheruses}}

'''''This Land''''' was a [[Canada|Canadian]] television series, which aired from [[1970]] to [[1986]] on [[CBC Television]]. Evolving from the earlier series '''''This Land of Ours''''', a documentary series about Canada's [[agriculture|agricultural]] and [[natural resources|natural]] resources, ''This Land'' expanded its focus to include [[natural environment|environmental]] and [[Conservation ecology|conservation]] issues.

Hosts of the show included [[John Hopkins (Canadian journalist)|John Hopkins]], [[Phyllis Gorman]], [[Laurie Jennings]], [[Mary Chapman]], [[John Foster (Canadian journalist)|John Foster]], [[Mike Halleran]] and [[Don Francks]].

